arts.ttl: Josef Martínez scores one minute after Petar Musa’s go-ahead goal to help Earthquakes tie Dallas 2-2
arts.sum: Josef Martínez scored one minute after Petar Musa gave Dallas the lead late in the second half with his second goal of the night to help the San Jose Earthquakes earn a 2-2 draw on Wednesday. San Jose (7-8-8) grabbed the lead in the 21st minute when Ian Harkes used assists from Martínez and Cristian Arango to score his second goal.
